    // egg festival
    "john.spring13": "Every town has their own version of the spring Egg Festival.#$b#What's funny though, is eggs have no real symbolic significance to this festival.#$b#Funny how culture develops huh?$1#$e#The rabbit though, it's pretty imporant symbolically.#$b#Not really sure how eggs got involved actually.$3",
