    "John_Introduction_Default": "You're that fella at %farm?#$eDon't overwork yourself okay?$2",
    "John_danceRejection_Default": "Oh... Oh, no thank you.$7",
    "John_divorced_Default": "Please, I can't stand the sight of you.$2",
    "John_breakUp_Default": "Oh...#$b#I understand, I'm not exactly a spring chicken anymore.$2",
    "John_Resort_Entering_Default": "The air is so clean here.#$e#I could stay here all week but I don't have that kind of money.$1",
    "John_Resort_Leaving_Default": "I think I need to lay down.#$b#The island is beautiful but it's not very disability friendly.#$e#I'm so tired.$2",
    "John_Resort_Leaving_2_Default": "There's too much sand in too many places.#$e#This is why I should wear pants to the island, but everytime I convince myself to wear shorts.$1",
    "John_Resort_Shore_Default": "The ocean is sort of scary isn't it?$2#$b#Still very beautiful though.$1",
    "John_Resort_Shore_2_Default": "I'm really glad I moved to Pelican town.$1#$b#I've been feeling much better lately.$1",
    "John_Resort_Umbrella_Default": "It's great there's umbrellas available. #$b#It's not the best idea to stay in direct sunlight all day.$1",
    "John_Resort_Umbrella_2_Default": "I saw Robin sunbathing a little while  ago.#$e#She's pretty, the sun makes her hair even redder.$4",
    "John_Resort_Umbrella_3_Default": "I hope there's scuba diving sessions here.$1#$b#I used to go diving whenever I had free time in Zuzu.#$b#It's a lot of fun.$1",
    "John_Resort_Wander_Default": "After the tide recedes, you can find a lot of shells and critters.#$b#I like picking up shells but the sea life I toss back into the water.$1",
    "John_Resort_Bar_Default": "I don't overdo it with alcohol, but I do like some wine every day.",
    "John_Resort_Default": "Have you met little Leo yet?#$b#He's so sweet, I like talking to him sometimes. $1",
    "John_Mon_Default": "Hm…?#$b#Oh, I didn't notice you there @.#$b#Hope your days going well.$2",
    "John_Tue_Default": "%You can hear John softly singing to himself.#$b#There's something very healing about music isn't there?$1#$b#When I'm feeling unwell, music is my go to for feeling better.$1",
    "John_Wed_Default": "It's a beautiful day...#$e#I'd rather enjoy it alone.$#$b#Sorry that was rude, I just need some time to myself.$3#$b#Gus was very talkative early this morning.$2",
    "John_Thu_Default": "Hey @!$1#$b#It's been a pretty great day so far, I got to visit with Marnie and pet her cows.$1#$b#I've always loved animals.",
    "John_Fri_Default": "You look... thirsty.#$e#Here, you can have this. [350]#$e#You should carry a bottle of water with you.#$b#Dehydration can be very dangerous.$3",
    "John_Sat_Default": "The weekends always drag on don't they?.#$b#But I sort of like that actually.$1#$b#I kind of process things differently, so the slower day gives me plenty of time to think.$1 ",
    "John_Sun_Default": "I've been meaning to visit the shrine, but I can't bring myself to.$2#$e#I just feel kind of lost right now I guess.#$b#But I still believe I think, I've the heart of a preacher afterall.$1",
    "John_Mon_summer_Default": "It's gotten quite hot.#$b#I can't stand the heat.$2#$e#I don't have fully functioning sweat glands, So instead of sweating I just end up with heat exhaustion. $3",
    "John_Tue_summer_Default": "I'm planning a road trip to Zuzu pretty soon.#$b#The sisters I used to work with wanted to talk to me.$1 ",
    "John_Wed_summer_Default": "It's hard finding out who I am.#$b#I became a preacher in my mid twenties, it's honestly all I know.",
    "John_Thu_summer_Default": "It's crazy how often you talk to me.$1#$b#I really enjoy it though, it's nice to have someone to talk to occasionally.$1",
    "John_Fri_summer_Default": "The second story of the saloon is pretty comfortable.$1#$b#I just really hate that I have to climb a ladder to get to my room.$2#$b#Really wears me out.$3",
    "John_Sat_summer_Default": "It's nearly Sunday, on Saturday I'd be writing the next morning's sermon.$2#$b#I kinda of miss it actually.$3",
    "John_Sun_summer_Default": "Robin is very talented. #$b#She builds house upgrades all by herself.#$b#Bet she's pretty strong.$1",
    "John_Mon_fall_Default": "Fall is such a great season.$3#$b#It really is just the perfect weather for me usually.$1",
    "John_Tue_fall_Default": "I could use a cup of hot coffee, don't tell Gus but he makes pretty weak coffee.#$b$It's very watered down.$2",
    "John_Wed_fall_Default": "I'm always in a better mood during this season.#$e#I get pretty cranky when I'm too hot.$1#$b#I really admire you in that regard.#$b#Bet nothing stops you from doing things.$1",
    "John_Thu_fall_Default": "Feel that cool breeze?#$e#It's refreshing, isn't it?#$b#A crisp morning always makes me happier.$1",
    "John_Fri_fall_Default": "The week went by so quickly, I don't know what happened.$6#$b#But that's okay I guess, just one day closer to the rest of our lives right?$1",
    "John_Sat_fall_Default": "I heard from Guther, that the woods have a lot of knowledge hidden within its land.#$b#Not really sure what that means, but it makes me want to go explore the area.$1",
    "John_Sun_fall_Default": "I've been reading up on the ancient animals of Ferngill and it's incredible.$1#$b#I'd love seeing some fossils up close one day.$1",
    "John_Mon_winter_Default": "The snow is beautiful this time of year.$3",
    "John_Tue_winter_Default": "The holidays are stressful.$2",
    "John_Wed_winter_Default": "It's already winter. Feels like I just got here.$2",
    "John_Thu_winter_Default": "Think I'll hang around the fireplace tonight. It gets pretty cold in my room.",
    "John_Fri_winter_Default": "This is around the time I retired from my religious service.#$e#It wasn't too bad of a day either, I remember ordering pizza.$1",
    "John_Sat_winter_Default": "I could really use a cup of coffee.#$b#It's pretty cold today.$2",
    "John_Sun_winter_Default": "This cold air really messes with my joints, I should head inside soon.",
    "John_Saloon_Default": "I can finally relax.$2",
    "John_Saloon_Entry_Default": "Good to be back.",
    "John_Spring_12_Default": "I'm not sure about going to the festival. Crowds stress me out.$2",
    "John_Spring_23_Default": "Dancing has always been my strong suit, but I don't know if I'll attend the flower festival this year.$2",
    "John_Summer_10_Default": "The luau is tomorrow. I've no idea what to bring for the pot.",
    "John_Summer_27_Default": "I'm excited to see the jellyfish tomorrow.",
    "John_Fall_15_Default": "The fair is supposed to be a big deal. I'm thinking of going.$2",
    "John_Fall_26_Default": "Spirit's Eve is such an interesting holiday. You should read up on the lore.$1",
    "John_Winter_7_Default": "I would fish with the rest of the townspeople tomorrow, but I am terrible at it.",
    "John_Winter_24_Default": "Would it be disrespectful not to go to the Feast of the Winter Star tomorrow? I don't want to offend anyone.$2",
    "John_thanks_1_Default": "You really mean that?$6#$b#Well, thank you, that means a lot to me.$3#$b#Being in this town, not many people notice me.$2#$b#And if they do it's just gossip.$2#$b#But you're different.$1",
    "John_thanks_2_Default": "I won't let it happen again.#$b#Sorry for burdening you.$2",
    "John_haley_1_Default": "Oh...$2#$b#So you heard that too...?$2#$b#I don't know why it bothers me so much... It's not the first time someone's gossiped about me.$2",
    "John_haley_2_Default": "Well, yeah, of course it does.$6#$b#All people ever do is gossip. It happened in Zuzu and it's happening here.$2",
    "John_doctor_1_Default": "...$2#$b#I guess you're right.#$b#It just gets so tiring. I've been through so many tests and still we can't figure out why I'm in pain.$2#$b#But I guess anything helps in this situation.$2",
    "John_doctor_2_Default": "No... no answers?$2#$b#I can't just give up, I can't live without knowing why this is happening.$5#$b#",
    "John_doctor_3_Default": "It's a good idea. I would have to go back and forth to Zuzu since there's more doctors there.#$b#Thank you, @, I shouldn't give up hope so easily.$3#$b#I'll accept the help I can get.$1",
    "John_priest_1_Default": "You're right, I'm excited to try things I never got to before.#$b#It's like being young again.$1",
    "John_priest_2_Default": "...$2#$b#I guess you're right. I'm sorry.#$b#I just got carried away, I suppose.$2",
    "John_event_final1_Default": "I'm really happy you feel that way. Sometimes I worry I might be annoying you.$14",
    "John_event_final2_Default": "Oh, I guess I understand that.$14#$b#Everyone needs their space.$14",
    "John_event_final3": "You do?$14#$b#I... I'm so happy you feel the same.$16",
    "John_event_final4_Default": "Oh, I...$14#$b#I'm sorry if I made you uncomfortable.$14",

