    "John_Resort_Leaving_2_2_3_4": "I feel like I'm starving.#$b#I might have a late breakfast.$1 ",
    "John_Resort_Shore_2_3_4": "I found a sand dollar, I've always wondered what to do with them though.$1#$e#Maybe Coraline would like it…$4",
