    "John_Resort_Umbrella_3_2_3_4": "Isn't it interesting, that a new place to visit can be all you needed to feel better.$1#$b#I love the change of scenery.$1",
    "John_Resort_Wander_2_3_4": "I've been looking for sea glass.$1#$b#It's very pretty, I like making chimes out of them.$1",
