    "John_Resort_2_3_4": "This resort is very nice, but sometimes I get a very ominous feeling when looking out to sea.$2",
    "John_Mon_2_3_4": "Happy Monday.$1#$b#I know it's odd, but I've always enjoyed Mondays.$1#$e#Hey there…$2#$b#Um…Oh, well I mean, Monday is when I start planning my week.$1#$b#I love planning ahead and making list.$1",
    "John_Tue_2_3_4": "%You can hear John softly singing to himself.#$b#There's something very healing about music isn't there?$1#$b#When I'm feeling unwell, music is my go to for feeling better.$1",
    "John_Wed_2_3_4": "I saw Alex playing football by himself the other day.$6#$b#If I could I would offer to play with him, but honestly...$2#$b#I don't like sports much.$3",
    "John_Thu_2_3_4": "You know,every  thursday of spring  is a pretty important day of the week for a follower of Yoba..$1#$b#It’s a day for self celebration.$3#$b#I guess it’s Yoba’s way of telling us to practice self love.$1",
    "John_Fri_2_3_4": "Robin suggested I try wood burning, but I'm worried about getting burned.$2",
    "John_Sat_2_3_4": "Elliott has been writing this book and he asked me to beta read it.$3#$b#Not sure I'm qualified for that though.",
    "John_Sun_2_3_4": "Lately I've been playing with clay. $1#$b#I'm enjoying it quite a bit.$1",
    "John_Mon_summer_2_3_4": "I really enjoy how Pelican Town experiences all four seasons.$1",
    "John_Tue_summer_2_3_4": "I overheat easily, but I've a lot of great Summer memories. $1#$e#When I was a boy, my brother and I used to treasure hunt at Zuzu beach.$1",
    "John_Wed_summer_2_3_4": "I wish my brother would come and visit me.#$b#But, we've had bad blood for a while now.$2",
    "John_Thu_summer_2_3_4": "I never considered myself a family man; but since I've been babysitting Jas, I've started to like the idea of settling down.$1",
    "John_Fri_summer_2_3_4": "Jas must be so lonely being an only child.#$b#I was raised with my five other siblings; can't even imagine how she feels…$2",
    "John_Sat_summer_2_3_4": "I'm thinking about heading to the beach this evening.#$b#I used to swim in a team back in highschool.$1",
    "John_Sun_summer_2_3_4": "I can't stand that old man;George I think is his name.$2#$b#He's so needlessly rude.$5",
    "John_Mon_fall_2_3_4": "In Zuzu there’s this little coffee shop called Rosebud Cafe.#$b#It’s a really nice place and I love their fall themed coffee’s.$1",
    "John_Tue_fall_2_3_4": "The weather is just perfect isn't it?$1#$b#Fall and Spring both are very comfortable to me.$1",
    "John_Wed_fall_2_3_4": "I've always wondered if the old myths of the Ferngill forests are true.#$b#I've always wanted to see the Jacabowy.$1",
    "John_Thu_fall_2_3_4": "Fall is the best season to pick mushrooms, the forest caves become overgrown with them.#$b#I'm not a big fan of mushrooms, but I like flattening and drying them.$1#$b#They make cute bookmarks.$1",
    "John_Fri_fall_2_3_4": "Haley doesn't seem to like or trust me very much.$2#$b#I mean, as a young adult I was used to it but currently it really does feel awful.$3",
    "John_Sat_fall_2_3_4": "Have you ever tried felting?#$b#It's a bit difficult but I really enjoy it.#$e#Just be careful not to stick yourself with the needle.$1",
    "John_Sun_fall_2_3_4": "Have you ever had black Liquorice?#$b#It's one of my favorite flavors.$1#$e#Joja sells really good black liquorice ice cream.$1",
    "John_Mon_winter_2_3_4": "It's gotten so cold so quickly.$2#$b#Whenever I see the cows at Marnie’s; I really wish I could give them sweaters.$1",
    "John_Tue_winter_2_3_4": "Pierre’s has some of the worst coffee I’ve ever taste.$2#$b#It’s expensive to order out of town so, I just buy Coffee from Gus.$3",
    "John_Wed_winter_2_3_4": "Coffee is one of my favorite drinks, but if I have too much my blood pressure spikes.$2",
    "John_Thu_winter_2_3_4": "I once met this fellow in Zuzu city; he was such an odd person I’ll never forget him.#$b#He had such pretty eyes too; they looked almost purple!$1",
    "John_Fri_winter_2_3_4": "You don't get snow like this in Zuzu city.#$b#The city keeps their streets and sidewalks clear during winter.",
    "John_Sat_winter_2_3_4": "When I was a boy, my father used to take me hunting during the cold seasons.$2#$b#It wasn't something I enjoyed, but my family was poor so we needed the extra food.",
    "John_Sun_winter_2_3_4": "My mother's favorite time of the year was winter and my brother's the same way.#$e#Honestly, they were very similar. $1",
    "John_Saloon_2_3_4": "I think Gus has the best coffee I've ever had.#$b#I might end up buying beans from him.",
    "John_Saloon_Entry_2_3_4": "Hey Gus, is coffee made?",
    "John_Saloon3_2_3_4": "If you stay for a drink, you're welcomed to keep me company $1",
    "John_Saloon4_2_3_4": "Sometimes I can't tell certain emotions apart, if I ever get confused please be patient with me.",

        /************************************************
    **  Dialogue 5,6,7
    ************************************************/
    "John_Resort_Entering_5_6_7": "What a beautiful day.",
    "John_Resort_Leaving_5_6_7": "I could use a nap, I'm so tired.",
     "John_Resort_Leaving_2_5_6_7": "be careful, don't hang out in the sun for too long.",
    "John_Resort_Shore_5_6_7": "I've been finding a lot of washed up jellies today.#$b#It's a bit sad honestly.$2",
    "John_Resort_Shore_2_5_6_7": "Sea glass is so hard to find for some reason, it's well hidden.$1",
    "John_Resort_Umbrella_5_6_7": "You're looking pretty sunburnt, need the umbrella for a bit?$1",
    "John_Resort_Umbrella_2_2_3_4": "Do you think the people of this island mind us visiting?$2#$b#I read recently that foreigners can be a pain for locals.$2",
    "John_Resort_Umbrella_3_5_6_7": "The woods around here are really abundant with resources, but if you're not careful you'll pick something toxic.$1",
    "John_Resort_Wander_5_6_7": "I saw the weirdest looking crab.$1#$b#I'm not completely sure it was actually a crab honestly.$3",
    "John_Resort_Bar_5_6_7": "I drank a star fruit drink and now my mouth is burning…#$b#Is that even normal?$2",
    "John_Resort_5_6_7": "I love the local architecture around here, it's incredibly naturalistic.$1#$b#I would love to live here honestly $1",
   "John_Mon_5_6_7": "@, it's great seeing you today.$1#$e#Hm?#$b#Oh, I'm doing fine, I've just been busy with my studies.$1",
   "John_Tue_5_6_7": "Lately I've been feeling happier, I've even gotten motivated to study the book of Yoba again.$1#$b#It's surprising, I didn't think it would hit the same way.$2",
   "John_Wed_5_6_7": "People seem to have some very negative feelings towards Pam.$1#$b#I understand why though…$2#$b#I guess I'm soft on her cause she reminds me of mother.$1",
   "John_Thu_5_6_7": "I went and checked out that old house of worship that Lewis told me about.#$b#It's really run down, but I can see potential.$1",
   "John_Fri_5_6_7": "My brother called me last night.#$b#It was an awkward conversation, but I’m happy he’s doing well.$1",
   "John_Sat_5_6_7": "Recently, I’ve been thinking about the story of creation.#$b#It’s shockingly similar to an older legend from Gotoro.#$b#Maybe our cultures are more connected than we thought.$1",
   "John_Sun_5_6_7": "As much as I enjoy living here; I sometimes really miss the privacy a city offers.#$b#In such a small town, everyone knows everyone’s business.$2",
   "John_Mon_summer_5_6_7": "In the worship community, people often debate on where Yoba’s kingdom resides.#$b#Personally, I think it doesn't reside anywhere in a physical sense.$1",
   "John_Tue_summer_5_6_7": "You wouldn't believe what I overheard last night.#$b#Apparently people really do believe in monsters in this town.#$b#I don't know if I believe, but I guess I'll keep an eye out.$2",
   "John_Wed_summer_5_6_7": "Summer bears some of the best fruits in my opinion.#$b#Like watermelon!$1#$b#It's very refreshing.$1",
   "John_Thu_summer_5_6_7": "Sometimes I wonder what it would have been like to be an only child.#$b#But, I honestly I would have probably gotten pretty lonely.$1",
   "John_Fri_summer_5_6_7": "I find it pretty odd that Linus lives in a tent like he does.#$b#I'm sure Gus would let him stay at the saloon for free if he asked.$2",
   "John_Sat_summer_5_6_7": "I've never been interested in crime stories, but I recently read one that was very funny.$1#$b#This man tried to rob a store in a chicken costume, but as he walked out with the money he took the mask off for some reason.#$b#Got caught pretty quick.$1",
   "John_Sun_summer_5_6_7": "You look pretty strong, bet it's all that physical labor from working the land.#$b#I'd love to be that fit, maybe I should try farming too.$1",
   "John_Mon_fall_5_6_7": "I love Alex's dog so much, he's a sweet pup.#$b#You'd think with my allergies I would stay away, but it's never stopped me from petting our furry friends before.$1",
   "John_Tue_fall_5_6_7": "My brother keeps saying he's going to visit soon, but I don't think he ever will.$2#$b#He has a bad habit of doing the opposite of what he says.$2",
   "John_Wed_fall_5_6_7": "There's this really interesting museum of natural history in downtown Zuzu, I was really considering taking a trip to it.$1",
   "John_Thu_fall_5_6_7": "I was walking the river’s edge this morning and I found this old arrowhead by the water.$1#$b#I’ve always loved reading about ancient history and artifacts.#$b#I can’t wait to look up the stories behind it.$1",
   "John_Fri_fall_5_6_7": "Hey @, it’s nice seeing you out and about.#$b#You know, I was thinking about how weird I was when we first met.$2#$b#I’m really sorry about that…$2#$b#I was just really anxious at the time.",
   "John_Sat_fall_5_6_7": "Elliott let me read a few pages of his writing this morning.#$b#You know, I really admire his efforts to  create something.$1#$b#I try to write a story and I end up forgetting my own story arches.$1 ",
   "John_Sun_fall_5_6_7": "I hope I don’t look as awful as I feel today.$2#$b#I woke up in a lot of pain this morning, must be a pretty bad flare up.$2",
   "John_Mon_winter_5_6_7": "I can tell it’s winter by the way my joints sound off in the morning.$1#$b#It’s like a orchestra of snapping.$1",
   "John_Tue_winter_5_6_7": "Haley and I have been chatting occasionally.#$b#She’s actually not as bad as I thought.$1#$b#She has a quick mouth on her, but she’s actually pretty insightful.$1",
   "John_Wed_winter_5_6_7": "I noticed that Clint really has an odd perspective on life; misguided really….#$b#He seems to have a good heart though.$2",
   "John_Thu_winter_5_6_7": "As happy as I am living above the saloon, I really am considering buying my own land.#$b#I really would like to start working with glass again.#$b#I love making things from recycled bottles and sea glass.$1",
   "John_Fri_winter_5_6_7": "Robin is one of the sweetest women I know.#$b#She’s always the first to offer her help, such a beautiful soul.$4",
   "John_Sat_winter_5_6_7": "I couldn’t help but notice there really aren't a lot of kids running around this town.#$b#I suppose it makes sense though, the population is small.$1",
   "John_Sun_winter_5_6_7": "I saw something very strange last night…$2#$b#There was this odd, dark figure outside. It stood in the same spot for ten minutes straight and then it bolted down the sidewalk towards the beach.$2",
   "John_Saloon_5_6_7": "This place has really become home to me.$1#$b#And Gus makes such great food.$1",
   "John_Saloon_Entry_5_6_7": "Gus, I’m back.",
   "John_Saloon6_5_6_7": "I heard about this little town nearby.#$b#Thinking about visiting and checking it out.$1",
   "John_Saloon7_5_6_7": "Have you ever had lava honey before?#$b#It’s sweet and spicy but that makes it really good,",

     /************************************************
    ** Marriage Dialogue Spring
    ************************************************/
    "Rainy_Day_0_Spring": "The rain sounds so relaxing.$3",
    "Rainy_Day_1_Spring": "I wonder what animals think when it starts raining?$2",
    "Rainy_Day_2_Spring": "Make sure you wear a coat, you don't want to catch a cold out there.",
    "Rainy_Day_3_Spring": "It's so tempting to go play in the rain.$3",
    "Rainy_Day_4_Spring": "I'm ready for this weather to clear up.$2",
    "patio_John_Spring": "Don't you love looking out at our fields? Isn't it beautiful.$3",
    "spouseRoom_John_Spring": "Being retired, I'm finding I have way too much free time.#$b#What am I supposed to do with it all?$1",
    "Rainy_Night_0_Spring": "We should cuddle in bed, it's the perfect weather for it.$4",
    "Rainy_Night_1_Spring": "Did you hear that noise? I wonder what it was.$9",
    "Rainy_Night_2_Spring": "I might make some hot tea. It sounds good right now.",
    "Rainy_Night_3_Spring": "It's been raining all day. I wonder when it'll stop.$2",
    "Rainy_Night_4_Spring": "You're going to get drenched out there.$2",
    "Rainy_Night_5_Spring": "I heard a old story about the rain once, that everytime it rains it's a goddess shedding her tears.",
    "Rainy_Night_John_Spring": "I like watching the rain hit the collecting puddles outside. It's pretty.",
    "Indoor_Day_0_Spring": "If I ever start rambling about something pointless, please stop me.$2",
    "Indoor_Day_1_Spring": "I love you, @.$4",
    "Indoor_Day_2_Spring": "I still get bashful over our wedding night.$4",
    "Indoor_Day_3_Spring": "I've been meaning to start writing again, but I can't seem to find my muse.",
    "Indoor_Day_4_Spring": "It's amazing I found love so late in the game.$1",
    "Indoor_Day_John_Spring": "Think I'll clean up the house today. It needs it.",
    "Indoor_Night_0_Spring": "Sometimes I see shadows from the corner of my eye. It's real concerning.$2",
    "Indoor_Night_1_Spring": "The sunset was beautiful. We should watch it together sometime.$3",
    "Indoor_Night_2_Spring": "*mumble mumble*#$b#Hm? Oh no, it's nothing.$2",
    "Indoor_Night_3_Spring": "I'm more tired than usual. Think I'll turn in early.$2",
    "Indoor_Night_4_Spring": "I need some more hobbies. I'm losing my mind here.$2",
    "Indoor_Night_John_Spring": "Ever wonder what creatures come out at night? Makes me wanna sit out there and watch.",
    "Outdoor_0_Spring": "Do you ever look at the sky, just really look at it? It's inspiring.$3",
    "Outdoor_1_Spring": "Don't mind me, I'm just enjoying the day.$3",
    "Outdoor_2_Spring": "I could have sworn I saw something, but I guess it was just my imagination.$2",
    "Outdoor_3_Spring": "The farm is looking so good! You're doing a great job.$1",
    "Outdoor_4_Spring": "Living in the country is so different from Zuzu.",
    "Outdoor_John_Spring": "The air is so clean here.$3",
    "funLeave_John_Spring": "I'm heading out, sweetheart, don't wait up.$3",
    "funReturn_John_Spring": "That was fun, but I'm glad to be home.$2",
    "OneKid_3_Spring": "Can't believe I'm having children at this age.$3",
    "OneKid_2_Spring": "I'm always scared I'll drop the baby.$2",
    "OneKid_0_Spring": "I never was good with children... But it really is different when they're your own.$3",
    "TwoKids_0_Spring": "I'm so dazed - we have two kids already?$6",
    "TwoKids_2_Spring": "I hope our little ones like me.$2",
    "TwoKids_3_Spring": "I already took care of the little ones, no need to worry.$3",
    "Good_1_Spring": "I love you, @, you always brighten my day.$3",
    "Good_2_Spring": "Oh.... Nothing, I was just thinking about last night.$4",
    "Good_3_Spring": "I would love to go to the beach soon.$3",
    "Good_4_Spring": "I was finally able to write today. It's about time.$1",
    "Good_5_Spring": "I know I don't do it often, but I prayed today. It felt pretty nice.",
    "Good_6_Spring": "I was raised to believe there's a plan for all of us... It's a nice sentiment.$3",
    "Good_7_Spring": "I think I'll unwind with a glass of wine.$3",
    "Neutral_0_Spring": "It's... it's such a gray day. Bleh.$2",
    "Neutral_1_Spring": "I need more hobbies, I'm getting bored.",
    "Neutral_6_Spring": "Don't overwork yourself.",
    "Neutral_7_Spring": "Here, I want you to have this.[347]",
    "Neutral_8_Spring": "Here you go, sweetheart, this is for you.[351]",
    "Neutral_9_Spring": "I want you to have this. I hope it helps.[369]",
    "Bad_7_Spring": "I just... I need to be alone right now, okay?$2",
    "Bad_8_Spring": "Now's not a good time.$2",
    "Bad_9_Spring": "I think I'm going to lay back down. I'm feeling pretty low today.$2",
    "spring_23_Spring": "The Flower Dance is tomorrow. Are you ready for it?",
    "spring_12_Spring": "The Egg Festival is always sort of fun. I like watching the kids play.$1",

     /************************************************
